<taxonomicName id="4C67F1C9533CFFA5FCF3FBEDFBD2FB8C" baseAuthorityName="Mello-Leitao" baseAuthorityYear="1929" box="[885,1033,1046,1070]" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Hapalotremus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scintillans">
<emphasis id="B9135658533CFFA5FCF3FBEDFBD2FB8C" box="[885,1033,1046,1070]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">H. scintillans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
could be a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="4C67F1C9533CFFA5FE2FFBCEFCF5FBEF" authority="Pocock, 1901" authorityName="Pocock" authorityYear="1901" box="[425,814,1077,1101]" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Iridopelma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hirsutum">
<emphasis id="B9135658533CFFA5FE2FFBCEFD50FBEF" box="[425,651,1077,1101]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">Iridopelma hirsutum</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFF6F7BB533CFFA5FD13FBCEFCF5FBEF" author="Pocock RI" box="[661,814,1077,1101]" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" pagination="540 - 555" refId="ref6971" refString="Pocock RI. 1901. LXIX. - Some new and old Genera of S. - AmericanAviculariidae. J Nat Hist Ser 7. 8: 540 - 555. doi: 10.1080 / 03745480109443359" type="journal article" year="1901">Pocock, 1901</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
or 
<taxonomicName id="4C67F1C9533CFFA5FCDCFBCEFEB1FBCF" authority="Pocock, 1901" authorityName="Pocock" authorityYear="1901" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Pachistopelma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rufonigrum">
<emphasis id="B9135658533CFFA5FCDCFBCEFF12FBCF" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">Pachistopelma rufonigrum</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFF6F7BB533CFFA5FF54FBAEFEB1FBCF" author="Pocock RI" box="[210,362,1109,1133]" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" pagination="540 - 555" refId="ref6971" refString="Pocock RI. 1901. LXIX. - Some new and old Genera of S. - AmericanAviculariidae. J Nat Hist Ser 7. 8: 540 - 555. doi: 10.1080 / 03745480109443359" type="journal article" year="1901">Pocock, 1901</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
(Bertani 2012). Both species had field records indicating a strict dependency on bromeliads occurring in the Brazilian Atlantic rainforest (
<bibRefCitation id="EFF6F7BB533CFFA5FC40FB8EFF1EFB0F" author="Santos RL &amp; Almeida MG &amp; Tinoco LDS &amp; Martins LB &amp; Maia MG" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" pagination="153 - 157" refId="ref7125" refString="Santos RL, Almeida MG, Tinoco LDS, Martins LB, Maia MG. 2004. Biogeography and conservation of the bromeliad tarantula Pachistopelma rufonigrum (Araneae, Theraphosidae) in Rio Grande do Norte, Brazil. J Bromeliad Soc. 54: 153 - 157." type="journal article" year="2004">Santos et al. 2004</bibRefCitation>
; Bertani 2012). 
<taxonomicName id="4C67F1C9533CFFA5FE27FB6EFD64FB0F" baseAuthorityName="Mello-Leitao" baseAuthorityYear="1929" box="[417,703,1173,1197]" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Hapalotremus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scintillans">
<emphasis id="B9135658533CFFA5FE27FB6EFD64FB0F" box="[417,703,1173,1197]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">Hapalotremus scintillans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was originally described under 
<taxonomicName id="4C67F1C9533CFFA5FF16FB4EFEC0FB6F" authorityName="Mello-Leitao" authorityYear="1923" box="[144,283,1205,1229]" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Dolichothele" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9135658533CFFA5FF16FB4EFEC0FB6F" box="[144,283,1205,1229]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">Dolichothele</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, but later synonymized by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF6F7BB533CFFA5FDE8FB4DFCD5FB6F" author="Raven RJ" box="[622,782,1205,1229]" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" pagination="1 - 180" refId="ref7039" refString="Raven RJ. 1985. The spider infraorder Mygalomorphae (Araneae): Cladistics and systematic. B Am Mus Nat Hist. 182: 1 - 180." type="journal article" year="1985">Raven (1985)</bibRefCitation>
. The general shape of the spermathecae presented by 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF6F7BB533CFFA5FE4FFB2EFD6AFB4F" author="Bucherl W &amp; Da Costa TA &amp; Lucas S" box="[457,689,1237,1261]" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" pagination="117 - 138" refId="ref5944" refString="Bucherl W, Da Costa TA, Lucas S. 1971. Revisao de alguns tipos de Aranhas caranguejeiras (Orthognatha) establecidos por Candido de Mello-Leitao e depositados no Museu Nacional do Rio. Mem Inst Butantan. 35: 117 - 138." type="journal article" year="1971">Bücherl et al. (1971)</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation id="EFF6F7BB533CFFA5FD6AFB2EFC43FB4F" author="Schmidt G" box="[748,920,1237,1261]" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" pagination="16 - 18" refId="ref7201" refString="Schmidt G. 2002. Dolichothele ist kein Synonym von Haplotremus (Araneae: Theraphosidae: Theraphosinae). Tarantulas of the World. 7: 16 - 18." type="journal article" year="2002">Schmidt (2002)</bibRefCitation>
of other species originally described under 
<taxonomicName id="4C67F1C9533CFFA5FE43FB0EFD8BFAAF" authorityName="Mello-Leitao" authorityYear="1923" box="[453,592,1269,1293]" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Dolichothele" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B9135658533CFFA5FE43FB0EFD8BFAAF" box="[453,592,1269,1293]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">Dolichothele</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, now 
<taxonomicName id="4C67F1C9533CFFA5FD1AFB0EFCA7FAAF" baseAuthorityName="Mello-Leitao" baseAuthorityYear="1923" box="[668,892,1269,1293]" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Hapalotremus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="exilis">
<emphasis id="B9135658533CFFA5FD1AFB0EFCA7FAAF" box="[668,892,1269,1293]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">Hapalotremus exilis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, is also consistent with that of 
<taxonomicName id="4C67F1C9533CFFA5FE98FAEEFD35FA8E" authority="(Bertani 2012)" baseAuthorityName="Bertani" baseAuthorityYear="2012" box="[286,750,1300,1325]" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Pachistopelma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rufonigrum">
<emphasis id="B9135658533CFFA5FE98FAEEFD99FA8F" box="[286,578,1301,1325]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">Pachistopelma rufonigrum</emphasis>
(Bertani 2012)
</taxonomicName>
. Moreover, the collector of the 
<typeStatus id="54DC34E8533CFFA5FF16FACFFF29FAEE" box="[144,242,1332,1356]" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C67F1C9533CFFA5FE9DFACEFDACFAEE" authority=", D. Bento Pickel" authorityName="D. Bento Pickel" box="[283,631,1332,1356]" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Hapalotremus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scintillans">
<emphasis id="B9135658533CFFA5FE9DFACEFE75FAEE" box="[283,430,1332,1356]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">H. scintillans</emphasis>
, D. Bento Pickel
</taxonomicName>
, is the same for the captured 
<typeStatus id="54DC34E8533CFFA5FC4BFACFFBF4FAEE" box="[973,1071,1332,1356]" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">holotype</typeStatus>
of 
<taxonomicName id="4C67F1C9533CFFA5FF16FAAFFDE1FACE" authority="Mello-Leitao, 1933" authorityName="Mello-Leitao" authorityYear="1933" box="[144,570,1364,1388]" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Avicularia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pulchra">
<emphasis id="B9135658533CFFA5FF16FAAFFE80FACE" box="[144,347,1364,1388]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">Avicularia pulchra</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="EFF6F7BB533CFFA5FEE4FAAFFDE1FACE" author="Mello-Leitao CF" box="[354,570,1364,1388]" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" pagination="171 - 173" refId="ref6533" refString="Mello-Leitao CF. 1933. A new theraphosid from Pernambuco and another, uncommon from Argentina. Rev Chil Hist Nat. 37: 171 - 173." type="journal article" year="1933">Mello-Leitão, 1933</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, at 
<collectingRegion id="49A344A8533CFFA5FDE0FAAFFCE8FACE" box="[614,819,1364,1388]" country="Brazil" name="Pernambuco" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">Pernambuco state</collectingRegion>
. Recently, Bertani (2012) considered 
<taxonomicName id="4C67F1C9533CFFA5FE95FA8FFE57FA2E" authorityName="Mello-Leitao" authorityYear="1933" box="[275,396,1396,1420]" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Avicularia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pulchra">
<emphasis id="B9135658533CFFA5FE95FA8FFE57FA2E" box="[275,396,1396,1420]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">A. pulchra</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="4C67F1C9533CFFA5FD10FA8EFCEDFA2E" baseAuthorityName="Bertani" baseAuthorityYear="2012" box="[662,822,1396,1420]" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Pachistopelma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rufonigrum">
<emphasis id="B9135658533CFFA5FD10FA8EFCEDFA2E" box="[662,822,1396,1420]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">P. rufonigrum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
due to its geographical distribution and colour pattern. For these reasons and all the generic characteristics from the original description, 
<taxonomicName id="4C67F1C9533CFFA5FD83FA4FFCC4FA6E" box="[517,799,1460,1484]" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Hapalotremus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="scintillans">
<emphasis id="B9135658533CFFA5FD83FA4FFCC4FA6E" box="[517,799,1460,1484]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">Hapalotremus scintillans</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is a junior synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="4C67F1C9533CFFA5FF16FA2FFE6EFA4E" baseAuthorityName="Bertani" baseAuthorityYear="2012" box="[144,437,1492,1516]" class="Arachnida" family="Theraphosidae" genus="Pachistopelma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Araneae" pageId="9" pageNumber="882" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="rufonigrum">
<emphasis id="B9135658533CFFA5FF16FA2FFE6EFA4E" box="[144,437,1492,1516]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="882">Pachistopelma rufonigrum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
